                <head>213. Editorial Note</head>
                <p>On June 15, the United States and the United Kingdom signed an agreement for
                    cooperation regarding atomic information for mutual defense purposes. The text
                    of the agreement is printed in Department of State <hi rend="italic"
                        >Bulletin</hi>, July 11, 1955, pages 63–64.</p>
            </div>
